    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is aimed to collect the following Serbia-specific epidemiology data on
      hypercholesterolemia: patents characteristics, patients' management/treatment and physicians'
      standard practice. In addition, the aim is to determine the proportion of patients on
      lipid-lowering pharmacological treatment who have reached the LDL-C and HDL-C treatment
      goals.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
